lead_paragraph: Mike Napoli singled twice and scored in his first exhibition game for the Cleveland Indians, who played to a 4-4, nine-inning tie with the Cincinnati Reds on Wednesday.

headline.print_headline: Napoli Has Two Hits in Indians' 4-4 Tie With Reds
